          <updateDate>2017-11-16T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Hospital Payment Fairness Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act to&nbsp;terminate the requirement for&nbsp;certain budget-neutrality requirements&nbsp;associated with&nbsp;the Medicare hospital wage-index floor to be&nbsp;applied&nbsp;on a national, rather than state-level, basis.</p>]]></text>
